counts](https://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/~stolte/R%2C+bird+data+WFS%2C+distribution+maps+and+grids) \n\n[Interactive statistical models](https://gammarus.shinyapps.io/ShinyWaterbaseNoordzee) \n\n[Shiny apps at NIOZ](http://www.rforscience.com/)\n\n",
